: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">document.body.scrollTop</span>设置为0，结果是页面一闪而过滚到指定位置，不是特别友好。我们想要的效果是要有点缓冲效果。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; line-height: 1.9; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">现代浏览器陆续意识到了这种需求，<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">scrollIntoView</span>意思是滚动到可视，css中提供了<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">scroll-behavior</span>属性，js有<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">Element.scrollIntoView()</span>方法。</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MpGQUHiaib4ib6j9X9s2kibfaicBLmIm6dUBq1YM6xzAOuiaQW3qCATvwcQCI9Hh21gicUUnZ0FFtbjdVoCQMIZjDBUaA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;) center center / 150px 110px no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-break: break-all; line-height: 110px; height: 110px; color: rgb(100, 159, 12); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">scroll-behavior</h2><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; line-height: 1.9; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">scroll-behavior</span>属性可取值<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">auto</span>|<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">smooth</span>|<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">inherit</span>|<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(225, 225, 232); font-size: 12px; font-family: monospace; color: rgb(221, 17, 68); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border-radius: 2px; word-break: break-all;\">unset</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justi